  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3 revision)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This revision elevates the Model Risk Level to 3 following a regulatory query regarding device classification ambiguity and expanded clinical deployment scope. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed and meet required levels. The 'Equivalency of input parameters' factor is documented as not assessed on the basis that the assessment team concluded it does not apply to a purely computational sensitivity study; however, the correct encoding for inapplicability was not applied.",
