    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors were fully assessed and all achieved levels meet or exceed required levels for MRL 3. The 'Equivalency of input parameters' factor was not assessed on the basis that the team concluded it falls outside the scope of a direct input-mapping study. All other verification, validation, and uncertainty quantification activities were completed satisfactorily. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met at all five operating points. The assessment team accepted the model as sufficiently credible for the stated COU.",
